<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Comment Hub</title>

    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/style.css">

    <link rel="stylesheet"
    href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.5.2/css/all.min.css">
</head>

<body>

<div class="container">

    <div class="hero">

        <h1>
            💬 Comment Hub
        </h1>

        <p>
            A beautiful Express + MongoDB CRUD application where you can
            create, edit, view and delete comments effortlessly.
        </p>

        <div class="hero-buttons">

            <a href="/comments" class="btn primary">
                <i class="fa-solid fa-comments"></i>
                View Comments
            </a>

            <a href="/comments/new" class="btn success">
                <i class="fa-solid fa-plus"></i>
                Add Comment
            </a>

        </div>

    </div>

    <div class="card">

        <h2 style="margin-bottom:15px;">
            🚀 Features
        </h2>

        <ul style="line-height:2;padding-left:25px;">

            <li>MongoDB Database</li>

            <li>Mongoose ODM</li>

            <li>Create New Comments</li>

            <li>View All Comments</li>

            <li>Edit Existing Comments</li>

            <li>Delete Comments</li>

            <li>Track Likes</li>

            <li>Express.js + EJS</li>

            <li>Method Override</li>

            <li>Responsive UI</li>

        </ul>

    </div>

</div>

</body>
</html>